defaultOpen.description: Determines whether the dialog is initally open. This is an uncontrolled equivalent of the open prop.

modal.description: Determines whether the dialog is modal.

onOpenChange.description: Callback invoked when the dialog is being opened or closed.

open.description: Determines whether the dialog is open.

softClose.description: Determines whether the dialog should close when clicking outside of it or pressing the escape key.
